Z","msg":"[超長文]區議會fact check，點解要叫人做選民？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1252404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1252404</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n踢走民建聯"},{"pid":"fbcce9f32407a51b07098467539a75a6faace025","tid":1252474,"uid":173849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:05:40.000Z","msg":"文宣組出場"},{"pid":"d0fd2ad0643258323cd1d6b7b529e90131f72fce","tid":1252474,"uid":126053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:07:23.000Z","msg":"女人之間都好大仇口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f589659678aec57595f6d783b778004654139451","tid":1252474,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:11:38.000Z","msg":"又吹風？"},{"pid":"20d1fd6117278af2a5c5ce219bf2a8420565787c","tid":1252474,"uid":197640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:16:13.000Z","msg":"又割<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751d15bbe29eed45b5c728e6db5142527cb1a71b","tid":1252474,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9578b983ca943155e11522cf4c04eb011a3a0bd","tid":1252474,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:29:14.000Z","msg":"長輩圖！"},{"pid":"207c687785d523a9b7690fa560790c6b4bf4fe0a","tid":1252474,"uid":138139,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:42:42.000Z","msg":"目前示威者方面沒有領袖，可能要由宗教領袖或其他「中間人」代為醞釀<br />\n<br />\n其實咁樣先好，無咁易比人捉，好似之前天琦佢地咁明顯既代表人物既話，一清算就實捉佢地諗住殺一儆百，今次直情想後期清算都唔知捉邊個好"},{"pid":"048c4148f57c713bf88d22825129ec29496bc4b1","tid":1252474,"uid":95221,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:45:03.000Z","msg":"「李慧琼強調，若單是調查警方當日行為，會得出偏頗結論」<br />\n點解嘅點解嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82bad2b3b5d24fafc00984d03a79f7acd88ffe9f","tid":1252474,"uid":14494,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:46:18.000Z","msg":"見有新post copy多次<br />\n<br />\n建制依家都轉緊軑收晒風話支持撒回同調查<br />\n<br />\n但留意番，暫緩同撒回有大部分香港人都袋住先，對港共政權黎講呢個決定其實不痛不癢，只係林鄭關乎面子一直唔肯撒<br />\n問題係佢地點會咁好死話成立獨立調查委員會係有得傾？已經有風聲講緊，佢地支持既前題係聯同監警會成立成件反送中示威期間既調查。而關於警方方面既投訴就沿用監警機制黎處理。咁呢個委員會仲會調查d咩？就係查番示威者中有冇用暴力行為黎幫定性暴動佐證<br />\n<br />\n小心唔好中伏，以為有賣港賊良心發現"},{"pid":"cc1e05e5282aedaf4954e87e217396dc706fe15c","tid":1252474,"uid":19278,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GqLUWUL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGqLUWUL.png&h=4a8a814b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚，和理非回合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aff148e16841f6eeccd67cc31837a660cec4591","tid":1252474,"uid":64159,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:48:25.000Z","msg":"文宣召喚！！！<br />\n呢個時候一定要大大聲屌民建聯辜負支持者期望啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc3932354628c8d59443c7363efff8845f837f4","tid":1252474,"uid":54303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d0fd2ad0643258323cd1d6b7b529e90131f72fce","tid":1252474,"uid":126053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:07:23.000Z","msg":"女人之間都好大仇口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:49:30.000Z","msg":"唔關事啦<br />\n民建聯淆底淆選舉咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4160e296567692ce2af7afe4c7