/><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4f281c4fbea1c7354e5f6983ba618f8378b08c","tid":1252474,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:03:30.000Z","msg":"佢話唔洗乜高官問責同唔可以放過義士有幾開心"},{"pid":"45baac4f29cb64ddc9c82480b7589af9a8aebcc0","tid":1252474,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:03:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8674a5b38c0b2215251fd48065c1ee32b6d4f38b","tid":1252474,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7d9e919132e07667f07b94d52066995cd9457ebb","tid":1252474,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:44:27.000Z","msg":"涉及《逃犯條例》修訂的爭議至今未息，民建聯主席李慧琼今早（23日）在無綫電視一節目上稱，特區政府在宣布「暫緩」修例時，已影響其管治威信；若政府如今認為宣布「撤回」修例有助修復社會，政府應更積極和主動回應市民相關訴求，民建聯的支持者亦會理解。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於需否成立獨立調查委員會調查6．12警民衝突，李慧琼強調，若單是調查警方當日行為，會得出偏頗結論；若更全面調查事件來龍去脈，則「要看屆時的意見如何」。她並不同意有建議稱，撤銷檢控當時任何人暴動罪，或是特赦所有當時涉犯刑事罪行者，因會衝擊法治這香港核心價值。她呼籲當前相關調查單位，應不論當時涉犯刑事罪行者的身分，公平調查。<br />\n<br />\n李慧琼亦表示，特區政府已為今次事件付出很大代價，她不認為要有問責高官下台，改組行政會議也未必有助解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n對有意見稱政府應及早跟示威者直接對話，李慧琼則稱，目前示威者方面沒有領袖，可能要由宗教領袖或其他「中間人」代為醞釀，此前也要社會氣氛先較為平靜；她亦認為，單是一次對話也不足解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n她又重申，民建聯今次並非「盲撐」特區政府；至於6月9日大批市民上街後，特區政府堅持如期推動修例，此後到6月12日爆發示威民眾跟警方衝突，則是「行政長官堅持繼續去吖嘛！」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190623/s00001/1561261485698/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e6%9d%8e%e6%85%a7%e7%90%bc-%e6%94%bf%e5%ba%9c%e7%8f%be%e8%8b%a5%e5%ae%a3%e5%b8%83%e6%92%a4%e5%9b%9e%e4%bf%ae%e4%be%8b-%e6%b0%91%e5%bb%ba%e8%81%af%e6%94%af%e6%8c%81%e8%80%85%e6%9c%83%e7%90%86%e8%a7%a3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190623%2Fs00001%2F1561261485698%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%259d%258e%25e6%2585%25a7%25e7%2590%25bc-%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%25ba%259c%25e7%258f%25be%25e8%258b%25a5%25e5%25ae%25a3%25e5%25b8%2583%25e6%2592%25a4%25e5%259b%259e%25e4%25bf%25ae%25e4%25be%258b-%25e6%25b0%2591%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e8%2581%25af%25e6%2594%25af%25e6%258c%2581%25e8%2580%2585%25e6%259c%2583%25e7%2590%2586%25e8%25a7%25a3&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=5fe908dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190623%2Fs00001%2F1561261485698%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%259d%258e%25e6%2585%25a7%25e7%2590%25bc-%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%25ba%259c%25e7%258f%25be%25e8%258b%25a5%25e5%25ae%25a3%25e5%25b8%2583%25e6%2592%25a4%25e5%259b%259e%25e4%25bf%25ae%25e4%25be%258b-%25e6%25b0%2591%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e8%2581%25af%25e6%2594%25af%25e6%258c%2581%25e8%2580%2585%25e6%259c%2583%25e7%2590%2586%25e8%25a7%25a3&h=ba30dc0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190623/s00001/1561261485698/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e6%9d%8e%e6%85%a7%e7%90%bc-%e6%94%bf%e5%ba%9c%e7%8f%be%e8%8b%a5%e5%ae%a3%e5%b8%83%e6%92%a4%e5%9b%9e%e4%bf%ae%e4%be%8b-%e6%b0%91%e5%bb%ba%e8%81%af%e6%94%af%e6%8c%81%e8%80%85%e6%9c%83%e7%90%86%e8%a7%a3</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K5FmCbK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK5FmCbK.png&h=0b052cf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d6cc7a20cf33169ae5ae4cada60ad35ff249cdf","tid":1252474,"uid":56115,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ko3Ljp1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fko3Ljp1.gif&h=16eee56c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"511cadd2180493b65b3aabfc111152d2b602b198","tid":1252474,"uid":59225,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0