":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:20:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>她又重申，民建聯今次並非「盲撐」特區政府；至於6月9日大批市民上街後，特區政府堅持如期推動修例，此後到6月12日爆發示威民眾跟警方衝突，則是「行政長官堅持繼續去吖嘛！」。</blockquote><br />\n梗係啦 一陣啲票無晒點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eda030edde0e101e3c73d670b8256793da1127a","tid":1252474,"uid":265702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:21:28.000Z","msg":"佢真係驚d票會走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n車 你呀爺會幫你架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaee5762d107da0c7ab916d08f31cfb97dfb324f","tid":1252474,"uid":167832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:22:14.000Z","msg":"識時務者為俊傑"},{"pid":"bf1ad103f5ae08388a024444c9b1fb44f978b34d","tid":1252474,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:23:06.000Z","msg":"想點撚樣呀"},{"pid":"ef06483505d55c536c7dd7330b3f460ec63f4bb6","tid":1252474,"uid":45376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:23:14.000Z","msg":"又想成功爭取"},{"pid":"22167f3640e0910965d27929d9d8e88017a0d205","tid":1252474,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:23:29.000Z","msg":"她並不同意有建議稱，撤銷檢控當時任何人暴動罪，或是特赦所有當時涉犯刑事罪行者，因會衝擊法治這香港核心價值。她呼籲當前相關調查單位，應不論當時涉犯刑事罪行者的身分，公平調查。<br />\n<br />\n支持查犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaafa9d920e1396d4c5d3a02ed280044c36efaca","tid":1252474,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQXj8Ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQXj8Ad.jpg&h=cd49b3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家經歷過這兩星期的抗爭運動都辛苦了! 雖然「五大訴求」(包括埋「林鄭下台」)仍然未達到，但希望大家趁呢兩日先好好地休息，之後重新裝備再齊齊繼續抗爭吧~<br />\n<br />\n不過，有啲事就真係比較急嘅，就係 - <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">距離今屆新選民登記嘅截止日期<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>仲剩番10日咋</strong></span>!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你自己、兄弟姐妹、同事朋友等等仲未登記嘅，請好好把握今次嘅機會立即登記，以便喺<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">今年24/11嘅區議會選舉</span></ins></span> 同 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: pink;\">出年立法會選舉</span></ins></strong></span>，將一個一個賣港又冇立場嘅親共政棍跟尾狗狠狠地踢出議會，將議會嘅否決權還番俾人民吧!!!<br />\n(可惜嘅係，已登記選民嘅更改資料期限已經喺2/6結束了，但大家仍需要覆查自己嘅選民資料有冇俾人更改／刪除咗，尤其係最近換咗新身分證嘅朋友)<br />\n<br />\n有關選民登記嘅資料如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">《地方選區選民》</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=2818f963\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">《功能界別選民及／或選舉委員會界別分組選民》</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=498ebe72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">網上更新電郵地址</span></strong> - <a href=\"https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/mainEM.jsp&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk%2Fosp%2Fra008%2FmainEM.jsp%E2%80%A6&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=e14f168e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/mainEM.jsp&hellip;</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">選民資料網上查閱系統</span></span></strong> - <a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=32243649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n此外，資料組嘅朋友可以好好地利用呢段時間，儲齊呢段時間來班建制狗所做嘅「好人好事」並作出整理，成為「彈藥」以供文宣組嘅朋友製作長輩圖及其他文案等，對一眾被利用嘅中年／老人家作出「反洗腦」宣傳，辛苦大家了！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>＊＊＊ <span style=\"color: pink;\">齊心登記</span>，<span style=\"color: pink;\">一齊投票</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">用選票拆散保皇狗</span> ＊＊＊</strong></span>"},{"pid":"0c24aa3e0efba9f12bd93a1d99bec1561f70bc40","tid":1252474,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:28:52.000Z","msg":"此後到6月12日爆發示威民眾跟警方衝突，則是「行政長官堅持繼續去吖嘛！」<br />\n又割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1136f41178bd9abb8972757362b614f532cc9a","tid":1252474,"uid":46464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:31:13.000Z","msg":"之前割得唔夠入所以啲要割深啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98dd53718882ee6c6a2d7b5356e59817866febde","tid":1252474,"uid":1643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a423edf427352d284cce1de41a760c8cd1863585","tid":1252474,"uid":135445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"908816cf12c925afc0b8e8b577381e15bc301ed0","tid":1252474,"uid":69472,"like":466,"dislike":1,"score":465,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:50:08.000Z","msg":"為左啲票可以去到幾盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:58:18.000Z","msg":"證明今次單野好多廢老都反<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:34:13.000Z","msg":"人地偷渡嚟，要遣返返去支那，臨老唔過得世，梗係反"},{"pid":"1cc6156570eb03d6aa3edeb14ce20759ce536209","tid":1252474,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:34:19.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家多d 留意一下<br />\n現時<span style=\"color: red;\">推登記功能界別選民</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n議會同街頭同樣重要</span>！！唔好比班仆街分化我地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請share 比多d 人士</span>，例如share 呢個msg 去<span style=\"color: red;\">十個post</span> 唔該晒大家！！！<br />\n<br />\n如果你合資格請去登記<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">功能界別選票比超區更有用</span><br />\n<br />\n同埋share 埋比你<span style=\"color: red;\">相關既朋友同事</span><br />\n<br />\n有一兩個界別需要大家<span style=\"color: red;\">自發組隊去游說</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家可盡一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(重開) [整合] 所有29個功能界別選民資格 (合共35席)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243657</a><br />\n<br />\n[再整合] 所有29個功能界別 (連超區) 選民資格 (合共35席)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245544</a>"},{"pid":"f507943cad382510481e1fc775a41aa122af06de","tid":1252474,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"尚書大人風吹邊面就擺邊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341d052d4e6e56054a1c367c444b61001608bcf0","tid":1252474,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:36:30.000Z","msg":"她又重申，民建聯<strong>今次</strong>並非「盲撐」特區政府"},{"pid":"00e4c7ebc31e13e7def4b86a08d3e78969fa17be","tid":1252474,"uid":68285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:37:47.000Z","msg":"反《逃犯條例》修訂遊行群情洶湧，至晚上9時許，龍尾才到達終點。民陣則公佈有103萬人參加遊行，創97回歸後的歷史新高。<br />\n<br />\n不過，有政府消息人士就表示，今次史上罕有的遊行，並不會動搖港府修例的意志。<br />\n<br />\n全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳則分析，今次遊行人數達到罕有之多，是有外力因素影響，惟效果只會是令中央政府更加警惕，不會讓步。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701ac9fc46b679bf140ae17d5c9274e39894293b","tid":1252474,"uid":50301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0eda030edde0e101e3c73d670b8256793da1127a","tid":1252474,"uid":265702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:21:28.000Z","msg":"佢真係驚d票會走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n車 你呀爺會幫你架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:39:04.000Z","msg":"淺藍中間遊離票冇哂"},{"pid":"20fad7729be4be3463f2514cbeb9bd6fa0f461f0","tid":1252474,"uid":34065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:42:06.000Z","msg":"民建聯乜鳩都支持  垃圾保皇支那狗黨<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/64824511_2284616218321195_3598279706023034880_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_oc=AQmzxQSvgAxPqadDCi38C6Hl071njNTNmDiqO4ttB4DDoGO8syPimstwcCGCcTVIS_4&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=44253c8fefb2d87d1846d7cb36ab0f0f&amp;oe=5D8741C5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F64824511_2284616218321195_3598279706023034880_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_oc%3DAQmzxQSvgAxPqadDCi38C6Hl071njNTNmDiqO4ttB4DDoGO8syPimstwcCGCcTVIS_4%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D44253c8fefb2d87d1846d7cb36ab0f0f%26oe%3D5D8741C5&h=08d3223d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f9a5799bae9552b9f0d5ede2e8f97cdc4d8334d","tid":1252474,"uid":72629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"701ac9fc46b679bf140ae17d5c9274e39894293b","tid":1252474,"uid":50301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0eda030edde0e101e3c73d670b8256793da1127a","tid":1252474,"uid